App Name: League of Coaching

Description
This application is used to help professional coaches on league of legends teams to coach their team. It allows them to monitor the player's games (seeing their activity and performance) and gives them data to help them provide strategic feedback.

Purpose
Coaching within League of Legends is demanding because a Coach needs to prove their value to the team continually. Being able to observe the user's activity allows the Coach to perform a systematic review.
